The membership access is granted to 1 IP Address. (we can upscale this if you need, free access to your wife,kids please contact us) Any abuse or sharing your login information ends with you membership.

    Gnoppix Code of Conduct : copyrights/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md at main · gnoppix/copyrights · GitHub

    Gnoppix email policy copyrights/EMAIL at main · gnoppix/copyrights · GitHub

The limitation of one IP address is not based on the operating system. It's a limitation imposed by the services you are using. You can install the Gnoppix image on 1000 devices without issue. However, services like the lifetime WireGuard VPN are restricted to one connection per device. 

Similarly, if we gain enough members to resume the OpenAI AI API service, it will likely have usage limits. You are welcome to use our API service, which is included in the "PRO" version. And of course everyone is welcome to support the idea, with a donation this keep our services running. 
Why is this important?

Open source software is essential to the modern world. It powers everything from the websites we visit to the operating systems we use. However, open source development can be challenging. Developers often work on projects in their spare time, and it can be difficult to find the resources needed to support development.

Our membership program is a way for people to show their support for our project and help us to continue developing and improving it. We believe that this program will be a benefit to both members and the project as a whole.

Thank you for your support!
